(1, 'upload/about-us-image/img_1620285443_609398039d9e7.jpg', 'About Us', '<p>Founded in 2002 by Mohammed Islam, Home &amp; Habitat Realty has been a cornerstone in the Jackson Heights/East Elmhurst/Queens community. Selling over $700m&nbsp;in real estate since inception, Home &amp; Habitat Realty has been able to provide sellers and buyers with quality service and insight that has allowed them to stand apart from their competitors. We specialize in single &amp; multifamily homes, coops, and condos. To better assist you, our team is fluent in Spanish, Bengali, Hindi, Panjabi, and Urdu. We service Queens, Brooklyn, the Bronx, Manhattan, Nassau, and Westchester counties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our Commitment:</strong>&nbsp;We promise to provide our clients with honesty, integrity, and transparency. We are committed to providing you with the best possible real estate experience by fully utilizing our extensive knowledge and network of professionals.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>ABOUT HOME &amp; HABITAT REALTY CORP.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Home &amp; Habitat Realty, we are fully dedicated to our clients. Whether you are a property owner, tenant, or buyer, we value your business and will provide you with the individual attention and service you deserve. We believe in a strict Code of Ethics. We believe in integrity, commitment to excellence, a professional attitude, and personalized care.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>EXCEEDING EXPECTATIONS FOR OVER 20 YEARS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Home &amp; Habitat Realty is a boutique real estate firm with sophisticated market knowledge. &nbsp;We service our clientele by devoting time, effort, and energy to a particular undertaking of their expectations to achieve worthwhile results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Home &amp; Habitat Realty is a highly regarded Queens realty firm with a unique perspective: we believe that real estate in&nbsp;Jackson Heights&nbsp;historic district &amp; Queens is about more than bricks and mortar &hellip; it&rsquo;s about people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your needs are the driving force behind everything we do at Home &amp; Habitat Realty. Whether you are buying, selling or renting, we manage both the practical and emotional issues inherent in all Queens &amp; Jackson Heights real estate&nbsp;listings with complete transparency. We offer financial guidance, assess life-cycle issues and help you with risk management. This incomparable personalized service has helped us exceed client expectations for over two decades and we continue to look forward to servicing your needs and making your dream a reality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re looking to relocate out of Queens and into a different part of the country, or the world, rest assured that we can help you. Our company has offices all across America and throughout the world so no matter where you&rsquo;re planning to go, we can connect you with one of our trusted referral partners in order to make sure that we help streamline your transition.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you need a referral at this time, feel free to fill out the form below and we will get in touch with you ASAP. Thanks 🙂</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Home &amp; Habitat Realty is a group of friendly, service driven real estate agents in Queens NY. Our team members are not only experts at what they do, but more importantly, they are driven by their desire to help people. This results in a service driven approach that places client interests above all else. The team approach is what truly separates us from the average Queens Realtor because while most agents are one person doing many things, we have several people doing one thing and being GREAT at it. This ensures expertise throughout all stages of the transaction and allows us to provide the superior level service our clients deserve. Rest assured, when you work with the Home &amp; Habitat Realty, you&rsquo;ll be in good hands with people who care!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Our Mission</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>To help people make good real estate decisions by providing expert advice, valuable resources, and connections to trusted professionals.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Our Vision</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>To become the leading real estate team in Queens and the go to resource for our community&rsquo;s needs.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Our Values</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We smile, because we love what we do.<br />\r\nWe study the market, because we are experts in our field.<br />\r\nWe treat clients like Family, because it&rsquo;s the right way to do business.<br />\r\nWe&rsquo;re successful, because we know how to get the job done.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Our Beliefs</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Learn. Serve. Lead. Succeed.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Our Perspective</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>That we are in the service industry with a specialization in real estate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here at the Home &amp; Habitat Realty we&rsquo;ve been very fortunate to help hundreds of families buy and sell real estate in Queens. The easy going approach we take, coupled with our hyper local expertise has fortunately made us a lot of fans along the way.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But don&rsquo;t take our word for it, below is a list of links to independent website reviews and ratings from past clients that we have helped in the past. One thing we can tell is that most of our clients are AWESOME people 🙂 Rest assured that when you work with the Home &amp; Habitat Realty, you&rsquo;ll be in good hands, with people who care!</p>', '<p>MON - SAT :&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;10:00 AM - 8:00 PM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SUN :&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Closed</p>', '<p>64-01, 35th Ave, Suite-1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Woodside, NY 11377</p>', NULL, 'Buyer Requirement', '<h3><strong>Buyers are required to provide the following before initiating any real estate services:</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (i) Prospective home buyers are required to show Government/State issued ID;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (ii) Broker agreement (agreement) required; <a href=\"https://globemaxrealty.bizoytech.com/assets/agency-fair-housing-bundle.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><em>click here</em></a></strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (iii) Pre-approval for a mortgage loan is required;</strong></h3>', '917-602-7564', '646-236-6044', NULL, 'mmislam64@gmail.com', 'mts74@aol.com', NULL, '<p><strong>Name:</strong> M. Minhajul&nbsp;Islam</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Email: </strong>&nbsp;mmislam64@gmail.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Phone:</strong> 917-602-7564,<br />\r\n646-236-6044</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Address:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;64-01, 35th Ave, Suite # 1,&nbsp;<br />\r\nWoodside, NY 113777</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://facebook.com\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://google.com\" target=\"_blank\">Google</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://linkedin.com\" target=\"_blank\">Linkedin</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://youtube.com\" target=\"_blank\">Youtube</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://whatsapp.com\" target=\"_blank\">WhatsApp</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://skype.com\" target=\"_blank\">Skype</a></p>', 'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100070425908145', 'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100070425908145', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'upload/header-footer/img_1675770546_63e23ab266516.jpg', 'upload/header-footer/img_1675770546_63e23ab26689c.jpg', 'upload/header-footer/img_1675770546_63e23ab266bbc.jpg', 'upload/header-footer/img_1620551562_6097a78a09cfb.png', 'upload/header-footer/img_1675770732_63e23b6ca40d5.jpg', NULL, '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3022.5227147308237!2d-73.90074788535321!3d40.750526643195954!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x89c25f05025b50b5%3A0xe0835b171e5ff72c!2s64-01%2035th%20Ave%2C%20Queens%2C%20NY%2011377%2C%20USA!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sbd!4v1675656520469!5m2!1sen!2sbd\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, NULL, '<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This statement serves as the transparency of homeandhabitatrealty.com in its commitment to serve the privacy of customers using the website. Please read through the document below to learn more about our privacy policy and how we use information collected from users and visitors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PERSONAL INFORMATION</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>homeandhabitatrealty.com does not require visitors to share personal information in the website unless downloading is concerned. When setting up a registered account, you as a member will enter information necessary to support us in contacting you regarding website updates such as new products and services. By providing homeandhabitatrealty.com with your personal information, you agree to the use of information in accordance to the privacy policy as outlined in this document.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NON-PERSONAL INFORMATION</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Upon receiving and therefore recording non-personal information from users, such as the IP address, cookie information, and requested pages, homeandhabitatrealty.com reserves the right to make use of such to modify website content. The website shall not connect any of these non-personal data with the personal information collected, as stated in the previous provision.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Upon allowing third-party companies to present advertisements via the homeandhabitatrealty.com website pages, the third-party cookie usage is subject to their own privacy policies not covered by homeandhabitatrealty.com, and we shall not bear any liability for such usage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>USE OF COOKIES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Visiting homeandhabitatrealty.com will send one or more cookies to your computer that uniquely identifies your browser. This helps the website log you in faster, thereby enhancing your navigation experience. Cookies may also help convey information about you and may be used by your browser for subsequent visits to the site. A session cookie is temporary and disappears after you close your browser, therefore closing once you reset your browser. You may refuse all cookies in your browser, however some features of homeandhabitatrealty.com may not function properly once this is disabled.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>INFORMATION SHARING DISCLOSURE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>homeandhabitatrealty.com may otherwise disclose personal information upon the following provisions: (1) To respond to any legal proceedings or court orders, (2) to protect the personal safety of website users or to defend the rights of the website as necessary, and (3) upon discovery of visitor actions that violate website guidelines as outlined by official terms and agreements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To protect the privacy and security of our users, homeandhabitatrealty.com takes reasonable steps such as requesting email addresses before allowing website downloads. Each user is responsible for maintaining security and account information, and controlling access to email communications with homeandhabitatrealty.com at all times. In the event that a user&rsquo;s personal information is compromised due to breach of security, homeandhabitatrealty.com will promptly notify the owners of addresses whose personal information has been compromised in accordance with homeandhabitatrealty.com notification procedures as set forth by this Privacy Policy, or as required by law.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>USER ID TRACKING</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>homeandhabitatrealty.com uses Google Analytics to track and analyze website traffic and visitor behavior and usage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On behalf of the homeandhabitatrealty.com domain, Google Analytics shall track the flow of users, their locations by country, languages, browsers, operating systems, Internet service providers, and devices used to access the homeandhabitatrealty.com website. However, homeandhabitatrealty.com shall not upload any data that allows Google to identify individuals nor their individually recognized IP addresses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CHILD SECURITY</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>homeandhabitatrealty.com takes child protection and security seriously. For that reason, we do not knowingly collect personal information of children ages 13 and below. For children under the age of 13, we do not recommend nor encourage sending personal information through homeandhabitatrealty.com, be it your name, address, telephone number or email address. In the event that homeandhabitatrealty.com learns we have collected personal information from children below the age of 13 without verification of parental consent, the information will be deleted from our servers as quickly as possible. If you believe that we may have information from children under this age, please send us a message via our contact page.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CHANGES TO THE PRIVACY POLICIES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>homeandhabitatrealty.com reserves the right to alter or modify the current privacy policy at any time, without prior notice to visitors and members, and therefore urges users to review the privacy policy on a regular basis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SECURITY</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Data is readily available online, however, homeandhabitatrealty.com assures its visitors and users that the website uses industry-standard SSL encryption to protect information transmitted on the website. Along with this, homeandhabitatrealty.com safeguards personal information from unauthorized access, network firewalls, and other security measures.</p>', '<h2>Terms of Use</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This statement serves as the transparency of homeandhabitatrealty.com in its commitment to serve the privacy of customers using the website. Please read through the document below to learn more about our privacy policy and how we use information collected from users and visitors.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PERSONAL INFORMATION</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>homeandhabitatrealty.com does not require visitors to share personal information in the website unless downloading is concerned. When setting up a r