chnology, and practices to keep clients safe in a COVID-19 world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some of the protocols that we are implementing include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The ability to meet clients virtually</li>\r\n	<li>Creating video tours to limit amount of in-person showings</li>\r\n	<li>Using e-sign platforms for the transfer and signature of disclosures, offers, agreements, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Limiting showings to serious buyers who have made an acceptable offer based on the video tour provided</li>\r\n	<li>Use of masks, gloves, and shoe covers for any in-person viewings</li>\r\n	<li>Providing a baseline online presence for all of our listings</li>\r\n	<li>Coronavirus waivers in order to protect all parties</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The safety of our clients and customers will always be paramount. We&rsquo;re committed to helping our clients buy and sell safely during COVID-19, and we&rsquo;re uniquely equipped to serve them during these challenging times.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rest assured that real estate is still being transacted, and we are taking all necessary precautions in order to ensure the safety of all parties. It is not business as usual, but we have adapted and are ready to serve.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>If you have any questions or would like to get started,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://localhost/Home-And-Habitat-Realty/consultation\">Schedule a Free Consultation today!</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://localhost/Home-And-Habitat-Realty/covid-19\">HOME &amp; HABITAT</a></h2>', '2021-05-09 04:07:06', '2021-05-09 04:25:40');

