(1, 'Useful Link', '<p>Founded in 2002 by Mohammed Islam, Home &amp; Habitat Realty has been a cornerstone in the Jackson Heights/East Elmhurst/Queens community. Selling over $700m&nbsp;in real estate since its inception, Home &amp; Habitat Realty has been able to provide sellers and buyers with quality service and insight that has allowed them to stand apart from their competitors. We specialize in single &amp; multifamily homes, coops, and condos. To better assist you, our team is fluent in Spanish, Bengali, Hindi, Panjabi, and Urdu. We service Queens, Brooklyn, the Bronx, Manhattan, Nassau, and Westchester counties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our Commitment:</strong>&nbsp;We promise to provide our clients with honesty, integrity, and transparency. We are committed to providing you with the best possible real estate experience by fully utilizing our extensive knowledge and network of professionals.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>ABOUT HOME &amp; HABITAT REALTY CORP.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Home &amp; Habitat Realty, we are fully dedicated to our clients. Whether you are a property owner, tenant, or buyer, we value your business and will provide you with the individual attention and service you deserve. We believe in a strict Code of Ethics. We believe in integrity, commitment to excellence, a professional attitude, and personalized care.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>EXCEEDING EXPECTATIONS FOR OVER 20 YEARS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Home &amp; Habitat Realty is a boutique real estate firm with sophisticated market knowledge. &nbsp;We service our clientele by devoting time, effort, and energy to a particular undertaking of their expectations to achieve worthwhile results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Home &amp; Habitat Realty is a highly regarded Queens realty firm with a unique perspective: we believe that real estate in&nbsp;Jackson Heights&nbsp;historic district &amp; Queens is about more than bricks and mortar &hellip; it&rsquo;s about people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your needs are the driving force behind everything we do at Home &amp; Habitat Realty. Whether you are buying, selling or renting, we manage both the practical and emotional issues inherent in all Queens &amp; Jackson Heights real estate&nbsp;listings with complete transparency. We offer financial guidance, assess life-cycle issues and help you with risk management. This incomparable personalized service has helped us exceed client expectations for over two decades and we continue to look forward to servicing your needs and making your dream a reality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re looking to relocate out of Queens and into a different part of the country, or the world, rest assured that we can help you. Our company has offices all across America and throughout the world so no matter where you&rsquo;re planning to go, we can connect you with one of our trusted referral partners in order to make sure that we help streamline your transition.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you need a referral at this time, feel free to fill out the form below and we will get in touch with you ASAP. Thanks 🙂</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Home &amp; Habitat Realty is a group of friendly, service-driven real estate agents in Queens NY. Our team members are not only experts at what they do, but more importantly, they are driven by their desire to help people. This results in a service-driven approach that places client interests above all else. The team approach is what truly separates us from the average Queens Realtor because while most agents are one person doing many things, we have several people doing one thing and being GREAT at it. This ensures expertise throughout all stages of the transaction and allows us to provide the superior level of service our clients deserve. Rest assured, when you work with Home &amp; Habitat Realty, you&rsquo;ll be in good hands with people who care!</p>', '2023-02-11 02:46:23', '2023-02-11 03:56:14');

